This archive contains documentation and sample scene files for
POV-Ray 3.0.1.  It can NOT be used without programs located in
another archive.  It is intended mainly for use by people who
are compiling POV on a system for which POV is not officially
supported, whether Unix based or not.

This archive is not needed by those people who already have a
complete distribution, such as the Linux, SunOS, DOS, or
Windows versions.

Questions and problems with Unix versions can be directed to
Andreas Dilger.  Please make sure you have consulted with a
local Unix person first if you think the problem is likely to
be on your end.  If you are installing POV-Ray in a publicly
accessible location, you must read and comply with the 'Online
or Remote Execution' conditions in POVLEGAL.DOC.

Andreas Dilger
Internet:   adilger@povray.org  or adilger@enel.ucalgary.ca
